{"type":"app","meta":{"headers":{"x-nextjs-stale-time":"300","x-nextjs-prerender":"1","x-next-cache-tags":"_N_T_/layout,_N_T_/page,_N_T_/,_N_T_/index"},"segmentPaths":["/_tree","/_full","/__PAGE__","/_index","/_head"]},"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\"en\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/css/783af4bc57ebee6b.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"script\" fetchPriority=\"low\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-4c9e6c08dcc7a301.js\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/4bd1b696-215e5051988c3dde.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/794-5fb6eff04a716ab6.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/main-app-201f14f4bcc9d480.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/481-54f2cadac433d5f1.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/app/page-4b239403b7778cd9.js\" async=\"\"></script><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&amp;family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&amp;family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;1,400&amp;display=swap\" as=\"style\"/><link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\"/><link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.gstatic.com\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"/><title>DemystifyAI — Breaking the AI information gap</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"The fastest, clearest way for non-technical people to stay current on AI. Curated signal — no jargon, no hype.\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico?603d046c9a6fdfbb\" type=\"image/x-icon\" sizes=\"16x16\"/><link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&amp;family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&amp;family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;1,400&amp;display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><div class=\"scroll-progress\" style=\"transform:scaleX(0);opacity:0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><header class=\"topnav\"><div class=\"container topnav-inner\"><a href=\"/\"><span class=\"logo-mark\"><span class=\"cg-monogram\">DA</span><span class=\"logo\">DemystifyAI</span></span></a><nav><a class=\"\" href=\"/discovery\">Discovery</a><a class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0.5;pointer-events:none\" href=\"#\">Courses</a><a class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0.5;pointer-events:none\" href=\"#\">Account</a></nav><span style=\"transition:transform 0.3s ease-out;display:inline-block;cursor:pointer\"><a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"/discovery\">Start exploring</a></span></div></header><main><section class=\"section hero\"><div class=\"container hero-center\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><p class=\"eyebrow\">AI literacy · for everyone</p></div><h1>The fastest, clearest way for non-technical people to stay current on AI.</h1><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><p class=\"lead\">Curated signal from the people building AI — filtered, summarized, and explained in plain language. No jargon, no hype, no scrolling through noise.</p></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><div class=\"hero-cta\"><span style=\"transition:transform 0.3s ease-out;display:inline-block;cursor:pointer\"><a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"/discovery\">Explore the feed</a></span><span style=\"transition:transform 0.3s ease-out;display:inline-block;cursor:pointer\"><a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"#why-demystifyai\">How it works</a></span></div></div></div><div class=\"hero-scroll\"><span>Scroll</span><div class=\"line\" style=\"animation:pulse-line 2.2s ease-in-out infinite\"></div></div></section><section class=\"section\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"stack\" style=\"gap:56px\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><div style=\"max-width:36ch;scroll-margin-top:80px\" id=\"why-demystifyai\"><p class=\"eyebrow\">Why DemystifyAI</p><h2>AI news that actually makes sense.</h2></div></div><div class=\"grid-3\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><div class=\"feature-tilt\" style=\"transition:transform 0.15s ease-out;transform-style:preserve-3d;will-change:transform;position:relative\"><div class=\"feature card-flat\"><div class=\"feature-mark\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.6\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"3\"></circle><path d=\"M12 2v4M12 18v4M2 12h4M18 12h4\"></path></svg></div><h3>Curated live feed</h3><p>Posts from the top AI minds — filtered for relevance, scored, and summarized. You see what matters, not the noise.</p></div></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><div class=\"feature-tilt\" style=\"transition:transform 0.15s ease-out;transform-style:preserve-3d;will-change:transform;position:relative\"><div class=\"feature card-flat\"><div class=\"feature-mark\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.6\"><path d=\"M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"></path><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"></circle><path d=\"M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75\"></path></svg></div><h3>Hand-picked people to follow</h3><p>A starter pack of the voices worth hearing — educators, researchers, product leaders, and builders.</p></div></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><div class=\"feature-tilt\" style=\"transition:transform 0.15s ease-out;transform-style:preserve-3d;will-change:transform;position:relative\"><div class=\"feature card-flat\"><div class=\"feature-mark\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.6\"><path d=\"M4 19.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 17H20\"></path><path d=\"M6.5 2H20v20H6.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 4 19.5v-15A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 2z\"></path></svg></div><h3>Curated skills &amp; library</h3><p>The best open-source tools, learning repos, podcasts, and videos — vetted and explained so you know where to start.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"section\"><div class=\"container\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><div style=\"max-width:36ch;margin-bottom:56px\"><p class=\"eyebrow\">How it works</p><h2>Three steps to AI clarity</h2></div></div><div class=\"props-list\"><div class=\"prop-row\" data-reveal=\"true\"><div class=\"prop-num\">01</div><div><h3>Discover</h3><p>Browse a live feed of the most important AI developments, curated daily by humans who care about clarity.</p></div></div><div class=\"prop-row\" data-reveal=\"true\"><div class=\"prop-num\">02</div><div><h3>Understand</h3><p>Every post includes context and plain-language explanations. No prior knowledge assumed — we meet you where you are.</p></div></div><div class=\"prop-row\" data-reveal=\"true\"><div class=\"prop-num\">03</div><div><h3>Apply</h3><p>Find tools, skills, and resources you can actually use, with honest beginner-friendly ratings and real recommendations.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"section\"><div class=\"cta-banner-wrapper\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><div class=\"cta-banner\"><h2>Stop scrolling. Start understanding.</h2><p>AI doesn&#x27;t have to feel overwhelming. DemystifyAI gives you the signal — clear, curated, and jargon-free.</p><span style=\"transition:transform 0.3s ease-out;display:inline-block;cursor:pointer\"><a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"/discovery\">Open the discovery page</a></span></div></div></div></section></main><footer class=\"pagefoot\"><div class=\"container row-between\"><span>© DemystifyAI · 2026</span><span class=\"meta\">Breaking the AI information gap · one curated signal at a time</span></div></footer><!--$--><!--/$--><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-4c9e6c08dcc7a301.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.